name: Flower in the night
description:
I took this photography while I was hiking on Kawah Ijen volcano, in Indonesia.

We were trying to get in the crater before sunrise, to see the blue flames the volcano is famed for. 

Besides the early hour, the conditions were just horrible: it was a cold night, at more than 2000 meters, and it had started raining 10 minutes into the hike.

In the end, we did not even get to see the blue flames, because of the humidity lingering in the air after the rain.

Still, I guess the trip wasn't a complete loss since I got a photography of this beautiful flower ;)
